OL,3,C'It's so important': Louise Thompson
OL,4,Cpraises Lego figure with stoma bag
OL,6,FReality star Louise Thompson has said
OL,7,Fa new Lego character with an ostomy
OL,8,Fbag is "so important" as she will
OL,9,F"help children engage in a dialogue
OL,10,Faround visible and non-visible
OL,11,Fdisabilities".
OL,13,FThe Lego figure has a scar on her
OL,14,Fstomach which sits next to her stoma
OL,15,Fbag, which is visible to toy users as
OL,16,Fshe wears a bikini top and shorts.
