OL,3,C'It's so important': Louise Thompson
OL,4,Cpraises Lego figure with stoma bag
OL,6,FThe former Made In Chelsea star, who
OL,7,Fherself has a stoma bag, hopes that
OL,8,FSara, one of the disabled figures who
OL,9,Ffeatures in the Lego Group's Friends
OL,10,Fsets, will help to educate people
OL,11,Fabout the subject.
OL,13,F"I think, to include a little
OL,14,Fcharacter like Sara, who's got an
OL,15,Fostomy bag ` so accurately as well,
OL,16,Fdesigned with the team of specialists,
OL,17,Fand also other stoma wearers to make
OL,18,Fsure that the bag's in the right
OL,19,Fplace, and the abdominal scar and
OL,20,Feverything.
