OL,3,C'It's so important': Louise Thompson
OL,4,Cpraises Lego figure with stoma bag
OL,6,FThompson, 34, who has suffered a
OL,7,Fstring of health issues since the
OL,8,Fbirth of her son Leo in 2021, revealed
OL,9,Fin April that she had undergone
OL,10,Fsurgery for a stoma, which Colostomy
OL,11,FUK describes as an opening on the
OL,12,Fsurface of the abdomen surgically
OL,13,Fcreated to divert the flow of faeces
OL,14,For urine.
OL,16,F"At home, we make a really big effort
OL,17,Fto try and normalise it around my
OL,18,Fson", she added.
