OL,4,Cpraises Lego figure with stoma bag
OL,6,FSpeaking about the Lego character,
OL,7,FThompson said: "I hope that people
OL,8,Fwith a stoma bag see Sara wearing like
OL,9,Fcool green shorts and a crop top, and
OL,10,Fthey think, 'Oh, my God, I can wear
OL,11,Fgreen shorts and a crop top, and
OL,12,Fthat's fine. I don't always have to be
OL,13,Fin a one piece, and I don't always
OL,14,Fhave to be fully covered up head to
OL,15,Ftoe.'
