OL,3,C'It's so important': Louise Thompson
OL,4,Cpraises Lego figure with stoma bag
OL,6,F"It makes me feel emotional knowing
OL,7,Fthat there are people out there who
OL,8,Funderstand how important it is to be
OL,9,Finclusive in the toy building process
OL,10,Fbecause, at the end of the day, toys
OL,11,Fare the entry point for a child into
OL,12,Fthe world.
OL,14,F"They're fundamental in their
OL,15,Fdevelopment. They shape their view of
OL,16,Fwhat they see."
